The '''Sandyman Family''' was a family of [[Hobbits]] from [[Hobbiton]]. They operated the [[Old Mill]].
==History==
The Sandyman family did not get along well with some of the other Hobbiton families, especially the [[Gamgee Family|Gamgees]]. [[Gaffer Gamgee|The Gaffer]] did not like [[Sandyman|the miller]],<ref>{{FR|Party}}</ref> nor did his son [[Samwise Gamgee|Sam]] like miller's son [[Ted Sandyman|Ted]], who collaborated with [[Lotho Sackville-Baggins]] and [[Saruman|Sharkey]] during the [[War of the Ring]].<ref>{{RK|Scouring}}</ref>

